<script type="text/javascript">
    $(function () {
        
    	if (window.disableCookiePolicy == undefined) {

    		var cookiePolicyId = 'cookiePolicyApproved';
    		if (!$.cookie(cookiePolicyId)) {
    			// Show the cookie policy confirmation
    			setTimeout(function () {
    				var cookiePolicyBanner = $('#cookiePolicyModal');
    				cookiePolicyBanner.show();
    				$('body').css('margin-top', cookiePolicyBanner.outerHeight() + 'px');
    			}, 500);
    			$('.js-cookieAccept').on('click', function () {
    				$.cookie(cookiePolicyId, 'true', { expires: 90, path: '/' });
    				$('#cookiePolicyModal').hide();
    				$('body').css('margin-top', '0');
    			});
    		}
    	}
    });
</script>
        

		<script type="text/javascript">

			$(function () {

				$('.regionButton').on('click', function (e) {
					
					e.preventDefault();

					var clicker = $(this);
					if (!clicker.hasClass('selected')) {

                        
						if (window.isIE8  || window.isIE9 || matchMedia(Foundation.media_queries['medium']).matches) {
							//  $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: 170 }, 200);
							var myButtons = clicker.parent().children('.countryList').clone();
							$('#buttonPanel').html('<ul class="countryList">' + myButtons.html() + "</ul>");
                                                        
							//Animate new button.
							var showList = function(){
								clicker.addClass('selected');
								$(".regionButton.selected").animate({'padding-bottom':29},100,function(){
                                    
									$('#buttonPanel .countryList').show();
									if (window.isIE8 || window.isIE9){
										$('.regionNav-expander .countryList').columnize({ columns: 4 });
									}
									$('#buttonPanel').animate({'height':$('#buttonPanel .countryList').height()+60},200);
								});
							}

							$('#buttonPanel').animate({'height':0},200,function(){
                                
								//Slide up nav button
								if($('.regionButton.selected').length > 0){
									$(".regionButton.selected").animate({'padding-bottom':14},100,function(){
										$('.regionButton.selected').removeClass('selected');
										showList();
									});
								}else{
									showList();
								}


							});
                            
						} else {
							$('.countryList').slideUp();
							$('.regionButton.selected').removeClass('selected');
							clicker.addClass('selected');
							$('.countryList', clicker.parent()).slideDown();
						}
					}

				});

				/* Store the window width */
				var windowWidth = $(window).width();

				$(window).on('resize', function () {
					if ($(window).width() != windowWidth) {
						// Update the window width for next time
						windowWidth = $(window).width();
						if (!$(window).isIE8){
                			if (matchMedia(Foundation.media_queries['medium']).matches || window.isIE8) {
                				$('#buttonPanel').animate({'height':0},200,function(){
                					$(".regionButton.selected").animate({'padding-bottom':14},100,function(){
                						$('.regionButton.selected').removeClass('selected');
                					});
                				});
                			} else {
                				$('.countryList').fadeOut();
                				$('.regionButton.selected').removeClass('selected');
                			}
						}
					}
				});

				/* END OF SPECIFICS*/
			});
		</script>

			$.cookie("homeAgency", agency, { expires: 90, path: '/' });
			window.location.href = destination;
		});
				
		/*SPECIFIC TO THIS PAGE*/
		var showPopup = true;
		if(showPopup){
			$('#countryModal').foundation('reveal', 'open');
		}
		
		$('.electiveClose').on('click', function (e) {
			$('#countryModal').foundation('reveal', 'close');
		});
		
	});

</script>

</body>
</html>
